r.s: Provides extra data structures and iterable/array functionality.
r.d: teds (Tentative Extra Data Structures) is a collection of data structures and iterable functionality
r.n: * Breaking change: Make StableMinHeap/StableMaxHeap stop inheriting from SplHeap to be more memory efficient. * Properly sort in StableSortedListSet::__construct and __set_state * Deduplicate code. * Reduce size/capacity limits to the same limits as array for Deque. * Add ImmutableSequence::map(), filter() * Fix bug in Deque::contains(), Deque::indexOf()
